parameters:
Kanae, while gazing at the cool and refreshing waterfall,
pours water generously over her body.

I don't have a bath, and the space is small, so I don't
have enough openness.

And so, she headed to the valley near the cottage that
had been discovered before, and after confirming that
no one was there, she modestly began to take a bath.
Kanae seems to be enjoying the bath after a long time.
However, her happy mood didn't last long.

Anyway, it's fine. I feel refreshed after a long time, so
let's go home now!
My panties are missing? No way...!
